data.name: Tumorotek
data.description: Web application that manage of biological samples utilized by hospitals across France.
data.subtitle: This intricate application enables users to oversee patient information, sample data, byproducts, and the associated cryogenic storage units. It facilitates tracking the location of each sample within the storage units, and provides an administrative panel for enhanced control and monitoring.

data.name: Biomedicine Agency
data.description: Web application that manages bone marrow donors and recipients, ensuring seamless coordination in the donation process.
data.subtitle: This application ensures efficient management of bone marrow donors and recipients, promoting seamless coordination throughout the donation process. Utilizing Java, Spring, TypeScript, and Angular, it offers a robust solution for the biomedical domain.

data.name: BranchIt
data.description: Manage tickets for development, designed to enhance and reduce development time

Creates a detailed Markdown file for each ticket, summarizing key details and analysis
and automatically creates a version control branch with the name of the ticket
